			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well, there is a really easy way of selecting yourself if you do need to heal during a battle, it is called F1.  Also, most healings spells are not meant to be used on yourself during battle, as either 1 of 2 things will happen, 1.)you will get hit and be interrupted.  2.)You will most likely lose more HP than the spell will give you back by the time you finish casting it.  Healing spells in this game are meant to be used after a battle to revive lost hit points, if you want something to save your ass in a battle, use Lay Hands, that is what it was put in the game for.  Also just for note, you get your lay hands once every day cycle, therefore you can use it once every 72 minutes.
				</font>
			</td>

